quran[18]{c,v,t,f}:
  37,94,"Basi (paŵapikene achinsyene isanamuyo) ŵam’bichilile ali nkutugala."
  37,95,"(Jwalakwe) jwatite: “Ana nkuigalagatila yankuisepa (mwachimisyene)?”"
  37,96,"“Kutendaga Allah ni juŵan’gumbile jemanjammwe ni yankupanganya!”"
  38,73,"Basi ni ŵasujudu Achimalaika wosope ŵene nakamo."
  38,74,"Ikaŵeje Ibulisu, jwalikwesyisye ni jwaliji mwa makafili."
  38,75,"(Allah) jwatite: “E mmwe Ibulisu! Chichi chinnekasyisye kunsujudila ajula junan’gumbile ni Makono Gangu ganagaŵili? Ana n’dikwesyisye kapena n’di mwa ŵapenani kusyene?”"
  39,58,"Kapena kuja kuŵecheta ndema jakuiona ilagasyo kuti: “Kungaŵe kwakomboleka une kuujila (ku duniya), basi ngajile kuŵa mwa akukolosya (masengo).”"
  39,59,"(Tachisalilidwa yanti): “Elo, chisimu ma Ȃya Gangu gam’bichilile, nambo mwagakaaniile, ni mwalikwesyisye, soni mwaliji mwa achimakafili.”"
  39,60,"Soni lisiku lya Kiyama tinchaona aŵala ŵaŵannambuchisye Allah (yanti akwete mwanache kapena ŵakamusyangana nao) ngope syao sili syakupiilila. Ana ku Jahannama nganikuŵa kwiuto lya ŵakulikwesya?"
  40,37,"“Matala ga kumawunde, kuti ngan’dingule Nnungu jwa Musa, soni chisimu une ngun’ganichisya jwalakwe kuti jwaunami.” Iyyoyopeyo yasalalisyidwe kwa Firiauna itendo yakwe yangalumbana, ni jwasiŵilidwe kwitala (lyagoloka), ni nganigaŵa malindi ga Firiauna ikaŵeje mu konasika."
  40,38,"Ajula juŵakulupilile ni jwatite: “E ŵandu ŵangu! Munguyani une nan’jongolele kwitala lyachongoko.”"
  40,39,"“E ŵandu ŵangu! Chisimu awu umi wa duniya uŵele chisengwasyo (chandema jannono), sano chisimu Akhera nijajili Nyumba Jakutamilichika.”"
  41,16,"Basi twatumichisye ŵanganyao mbungo jakusisima nnope m’moŵa gamakungu, kuti twape kupasya ilagasyo yakwalusya pa umi wa duniya, sano ilagasyo ya ku Akhera niyaili yakwalusya nnope, soni ŵanganyao ngasakamuchisyidwa."
  41,17,"Sano ŵanya Asamuda basi twajongwele, nambo ŵaunonyele ungalola kulekangana ni chongoko, basi chakwembekenye chikokomo cha moto wa ilagasyo yakwalusya ligongo lya yaŵaliji nkupanganya."
  41,18,"Ni twajokwele aŵala ŵaŵakulupilile nikuŵaga ni woga (wakun’jogopa Allah)."
  42,1,"Hâ. Mîm. ",footnotes:1:Asi harufusi ni chimpepe mu isimosimo ya Qur’an. Ni pangali jwine jwaakumanyilila mate gakwe ikaŵeje Allah pe basi.
  42,2,"‘Aîn Sîn Qâf. ",footnotes:1:Nnole chilaaki cha Ȃya ja {42:1}.
  42,3,"Mwele ni mwaakuuwulila (maloŵe) Allah Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwalunda lwakusokoka kukwenu (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) ni (yaŵatite pakuuwula) kwa aŵala (Achimitenga) ŵa paujo penu."